[C]Kan laitlang [Em]ram nuam i [F]lenti ve ding [Dm]hin, [F]hram len hmanh [G]ning zei san a tlai [C]lo[G], [C]kan hngak ko [Em]rih law aw [F]dingdi par dawh [Dm]te, [F]kan dawtnak [G]a dong ti lai [C]lo

